 and us via your medium and those of your ancestors who are Prophets and martyrs and performers of good deeds and good followers. May Allah not abandon us from this good fortune and recommendation Ameen! Salam from all the worlds on both of you! Allah’s blessings and bounties on you!", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "ASH-HADO ANNAKOMA JAAHADTOMA FEE NUSRATE DEENIL LAAHE WA HEMAAYATE I'TRATE RASOOLIL LAAHE HAQQAL JEHAADE FA JAZAAKOMAL LAAHO A'NHO WA A'N NABIYYEHI WA AHLEBAYTEHI WA A'NIL ISLAAME WA AHLEHI AFZALA JAZAAISH SHOHADAAE WA ANMAA HOZUZIS SOA'DAAE WA A'RFA-A DARAJAATIL ATQ'EYAAE. WA ALHAQAKOMAL LAAHO WA IYYAANA BE HAQQEKOMA WA BE AABAAEKOMASH SHORAFAAE MENAL AMBEYAAAE WAL AWSEYAAAE WASH-SHOHADAAAE WAS-SOLAHAAAE WA HASONA OOLAAAEKA RAFEEQAN WA LA KHAYYABANAL LAAHO MIN HAAZEHIS SA-A'ADATE WA SHAFAA-A'TE HAA-OOLAAISH SHOFA AAE AAMEENA YAA RABBAL A'ALAMEENA WAS-SALAAMO A'LAYKOMA WA RAHMATUL LAAHE WA BARAKAATOHU.", "ArabicText1": "اَشْهَدُ اَنَّكُمَا جَاهَدْتُمَا فِیْ نُصْرَۃِ دِیْنِ اللہِ وَحِمَایَۃِ عِتْرَۃِ رَسُوْلِ اللہِ حَقَّ الْجِهَادِ فَجَزَاكُمَا اللہُ عَنْهُ وَعَنْ نَبِیِّهٖ وَاَهْلِ بَیْتِهٖ وَعَنِ الْاِسْلَامِ وَاَهْلِهٖ اَفْضَلَ جَزَآءِ الشُّهَدَآءِ وَاَنْمٰی حُظُوْظِ السُّعَدَآءِ وَاَرْفَعَ دَرَجَاتِ الْاَتْقِیَآءِ۔ وَاَلْحَقَكُمَا اللہُ وَاِیَّانَا بِحَقِّكُمَا وَبِاٰبَائِكُمَا الشُّرَفَآءِ مِنَ الاَنْۢبِیَآءِ وَالْاَوْصِیَآءِ وَالشُّهَدَآءِ وَالصُّلَحَآءِ وَحَسُنَ اُوْلٰٓئِكَ رَفِیْقًا وَلَا خَیَّبَنَا اللہُ مِنْ هٰذِهِ السَّعَادَۃِ وَشَفَاعَۃِ هٰؤُلَآءِ الشُّفَعَآءِ اٰمِیْنَ یَا رَبَّ الْعَالَمِیْنَ وَالسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكُمَا وَرَحْمَۃُ اللہِ وَبَرَكَاتُهٗ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "A